@startuml
title Chapter 1 — Support Layer: Country x Topic x Year support tensor

|Input|
start
:ATCM Working Papers corpus (English);
:Preprocessing — clean, segment into passages;

|BERTopic stages|
:Embed documents (Stella, R^m);
:Dimensionality reduction (UMAP);
:Cluster (HDBSCAN);
:Topic representation (c-TF-IDF);
note right
  Output: topic set K,
  centroids mu_k, and
  per-document topic
  assignment K(d)
end note

|Our stages|
:Relevance gating — embed passages,
score rho_{p,k} = cos(e_p, mu_k),
select P_{d,k} above threshold tau;
note right: selection, not a weight

:Hypothesis bank — per-topic poles
h_k^+, h_k^0, h_k^- (contestability priors);

:Stance classification (NLI, Laurer 2024)
-> three-pole distribution -> 5-class pi_{d,k}
-> expected value s_{d,k}  [Eq. 1/2];
note right
  contrast lives in
  entailment vs contradiction
  across poles
end note

:Generative cross-check (quote-grounded,
Le Mens & Gallego 2024) — construct validity;

:Aggregation — sum over co-sponsored WPs,
attribution weight w_{d,c}  [Eq. 3];

|Output|
:Support tensor S (C x |K| x Y);
note right
  used as: prediction input (Ch.2)
  and agent state (Ch.3)
end note

partition "Validation (planned, no Stage-2 results)" {
  :Topic-convergence vs Secretariat categories;
  :CRAMRA minerals canary (same-axis recovery);
  :Network replication vs Botelho et al.;
}
stop
@enduml